        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "feat: add Skill Workshop Control UI",
        "body": "## Summary\r\n\r\nAdds the Skill Workshop Control UI: a dedicated place to review, refine, and apply agent-created skill proposals before they become live skills.\r\n\r\nSkill Workshop is now a first-class product surface. Users can see what the agent drafted, inspect the proposed skill, review support files, send revision requests back to the agent, and decide whether a proposal should become a real skill.\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1193\" height=\"683\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/aaf7dcf9-4a24-4c7b-8ff2-087945e05e54\" />\r\n<img width=\"1233\" height=\"906\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/24ec3293-d73e-4f4c-9d84-dae304eae3c3\" />\r\n\r\n\r\n## What’s New\r\n\r\n- Adds the Skill Workshop route and navigation entry.\r\n- Adds Board view for browsing proposal history across pending, applied, rejected, quarantined, and stale states.\r\n- Adds Today view for reviewing pending proposals one at a time.\r\n- Adds proposal actions: Use it, Tweak it, and Skip.\r\n- Adds real proposal loading from the Skill Workshop gateway surface.\r\n- Adds proposal search, status filters, empty states, and filtered proposal navigation.\r\n- Adds resizable proposal list pane with persisted width.\r\n- Adds support-file preview with search and keyboard-contained modal behavior.\r\n- Adds revision handoff into the proposal’s workshop session, with an option to use the current chat.\r\n- Adds stable Skill Workshop tool-card labels in live and refreshed chat transcripts.\r\n- Adds proposal origin/session metadata so revisions can continue in the right context.\r\n\r\n## Why\r\n\r\nThis makes Skill Workshop the user-facing review layer for OpenClaw’s skill creation flow.\r\n\r\nAgents can draft skills, but users now have a clear workspace for deciding what gets refined, rejected, or promoted into their live skill set.\r\n\r\n## Verification\r\n\r\n- `git diff --check`\r\n- `pnpm format:check ui/src/styles/skill-workshop.css`\r\n- `pnpm format:check ui/src/ui/views/skill-workshop.ts`\r\n- `pnpm format:check ui/src/ui/views/skill-workshop.ts ui/src/ui/app-render.ts`\r\n- `pnpm format:check ui/src/ui/controllers/skill-workshop.ts ui/src/ui/app-render.ts ui/src/ui/app.ts ui/src/ui/app-view-state.ts ui/src/styles/skill-workshop.css`\r\n- `pnpm --dir ui build`\r\n",
